* Set GunStart time for a specific race

* Purpose:          Assigns a starting time (GunStart) to all runners in a specific race.

* Param 1 (%1):     The race identifier (e.g., 5k, 10k).

* Param 2 (%2):     The start time formatted as HH:MM:SS.01.

* Example:          setgunstart.rsm 5k 09:02:11.15

select              Race
=                   %1
selected            GunStart
selected message    %2
